quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  68,34,"Inene\tokwabenzi\tbokulungileyo\tyiMiyezo\tyolonwabo eseNkosini yabo"
  68,35,Ingaba Siza kuphatha amaMuslim njengezaphula- mthetho na
  68,36,Kwenzeka ntoni na kuni? Kanti lunjani na ugwebo lwenu
  68,37,Okanye mhlawumbi ninesibhalo enifunda sona
  68,38,Eniza kufumana konke enikunqwenelayo (ngaso)
  68,39,"Okanye nineminqophiso (esisibophelelo) kuThi, eqhuba iye kuma kwiMini yoVuko, (ekubonakala) okokuba niya kuba noko nigwebe ukuba nibe kuko"
  68,40,Babuze okokuba nguwuphi na apha kubo oza kukumela ngenene oko
  68,41,Okanye mhlawumbi banamahlulelane? Mabeze namahlulelane abo kaloku ukuba bathetha inyaniso
  68,42,"NgeMini ubuqu buka-Allâh buya kutyhileka, ke kaloku baya kubizwa ukuba beze kuqubuda (kuAllâh) kodwa (abahanahanisi) abayi kukwazi ukukwenza oko"
  68,43,"Amehlo abo aya kuthotyelwa phantsi, bathiwe wambu kukuhlazeka; kaloku babedla ngokubizwa ukuba beze kuqubuda (emthandazweni) besenempilo entle (ehlabathini)"
  68,44,"Ndiyeke ke Mna (Muhammad Ndiqubisane) nalowo uyiphikayo le ntetho (i’Kur’ân), Thina Siya kumana ukubakhokelela apho bangaziyo"
  68,45,"Yaye Ndiya kubanika ixesha, inene elaM icebo liqinile"
  68,46,Makube mhlawumbi ubabiza intlawulo (ngalo Myalezo) ekucaca okokuba bazifumanisa benetyala elingumthwalo kubo
  68,47,"Okanye mhlawumbi banolwazi lokungabonwayo, abalubhala phantsi"
  68,48,"Yiba nomonde ke wena ngesigqibo seNkosi yakho, ungabi njengomfo wentlanzi (uYûnus) xa wakhwazayo ekwimo yonxunguphalo"
  68,49,"Ukuba kwakungekho ngenxa yenceba eyavela eNkosini yakhe eyamgubungelayo, ngewayejulwe elunxwemeni oluze enokusoleka"
  68,50,Ke kaloku iNkosi yakhe yamkhetha yamenza ilungisa
  68,51,"Inene abo bangakholwayo bebengakwenza utyibilike ngamehlo abo (ngendlela abakujonga ngayo) xa besiva umyalezo kananjalo bathi, “Inene yena ushiywe ziingqondo.”"
  68,52,Kodwa akunto yimbi oku ngaphandle kokuba sisikhumbuzi emazweni